description: Solar Alliance Energy Inc., together with its subsidiaries, provides energy solutions. The company primarily focuses on development, engineering, procurement, and construction of commercial and industrial solar projects, and residential solar installations in Tennessee, Kentucky, Illinois, and North/South Carolina. It also offers electric vehicle charger installation services; and backup generator, home inspection, commercial generator, renewable radar, utility scale power, commercial electric vehicle charging, and data centers solutions. The company was formerly known as Finavera Solar Energy, Inc. and changed its name to Solar Alliance Energy Inc. in January 2016. Solar Alliance Energy Inc. was founded in 2003 and is based in Toronto, Canada.
